menuModel

Class SavedGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • menuModel.SavedGame

  • public class SavedGame
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores all data for a saved game. This includes the name of the game save, the date when created, and all gameplay objects within the game itself at the time of generation.
    Author:
    Eric Liou
